			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I know this is an old topic but oh well...
<br />

<br />

<br />
I'm for legallizing mj for a couple reasons, 
<br />

<br />
1. maybe it affects different people differently but I get more of a buzz from just smoking Clove cigs(which are perfectly legal) then I do from mj, so why make it illegal
<br />

<br />
2. mj is a wonderful cash crop, for instance it is the number one cash crop here in oklahoma. there are a lot of poor farmers that can't make enough money to pay the rent selling wheat that could grow mj and make a good profit on the new market if it were legalized.
<br />

<br />
3. mj has the potential for making the government lots of money with taxes if it were taxed heavily like cigarretts are. and then the DEA could focus their attention on the truely harmful drugs like coke, heroin, or lsd instead of chasing around mj all the time
<br />

<br />
4. mj is no more addictive then alcohol or tobacco, and people are driving under the influence of legal drugs every day whether you know it or not.  I've seen people smoke mj all night w/out passing out from it, it is the  ones drinking the Legal alcohol who are staggering across the rooms hardly seeing straight. I agree that I would rather ride with a person who had been smoking joints for the last hour than a person who had been drinking alcohol for the last hour.
<br />

<br />
5. last point here... If mj were legalized the price would be driven down either artificially by the government or normally by the free economy. this would take a big bite out of the profit of various illegal sources ranging from the punk down on 23rd st. who sells a quarter sack for $40, to the gangs, to the mob/maffia, to the columbian drug lords. If suddenly you can start buying a full ounce for $5, that has already been processed and had all the stems and bad stuff picked out of it , down at the specialty tobacco store.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Any way that is my 2cp on the subject.<br />_________________<br />Tinuviel Nightingale
<br />
Maestro
<br />
Noble Blade
<br />

<br />
Why is it so hot in here, And what are we doing in this hand basket?!?</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
